  "text": "(iii) HIS4uas-ime1-his4-lacZ. In the following plasmids various portions of the IME1 5Ј region were inserted in the his4-lacZ chimeric gene by using the X-1 construct carrying the HIS4uas-his4-lacZ gene with a deletion from Ϫ181 to Ϫ202, leaving 2 Gcn4p binding sites upstream of a XhoI site [CITATION_1] . The following chimeric genes are carried on the shuttle vector YCp50: YCp1138, carries no IME1 information; and YCpAS334, IME1 (Ϫ449 to Ϫ227). The following plasmids are carried on YIplac128 (10): YIp2006, carries no IME1 information; YIp2032, IME1 (Ϫ915 to Ϫ788); YIp2055, IME1 (Ϫ788 to Ϫ756); and YIp2067, IME1 (Ϫ1202 to Ϫ1153).",
