      "span_text": "(iii) HIS4uas-ime1-his4-lacZ. In the following plasmids various portions of the IME1 5Ј region were inserted in the his4-lacZ chimeric gene by using the X-1 construct carrying the HIS4uas-his4-lacZ gene with a deletion from Ϫ181 to Ϫ202, leaving 2 Gcn4p binding sites upstream of a XhoI site [CITATION_1] ."
